@startuml
title Diagram Konteks (DFD Level 0) - Sistem Informasi Website Dispora

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 9
skinparam nodesep 40
skinparam ranksep 50

rectangle "Pengunjung\nWebsite" as user #E8F4F8
circle "   0   " as p0 #4A90E2
database "D1\nData" as ds #F5F5F5

note top of p0
Sistem Website Dispora
(Next.js SSR)
end note

user --> p0 : Request\nHalaman
p0 --> user : Response\nHTML
p0 --> ds : Query\nData
ds --> p0 : Data\nJSON

note left of user
Aktivitas:
- Akses halaman
- Lihat berita/galeri
- Unduh dokumen
end note

note right of ds
Data Store:
- news.json
- gallery.json
- programs.json
- ppid.json
end note

@enduml
